Summary: 4 silent objects go slowly to horizon
trends: There have been no other sightings in Stockton
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: sighting detailsi was at work (security) on a building site alone.i had left my cabin for a cigarette and coming from the west of me travelling east i saw a orange\red light.it was moving slowly but in a straight line maybe 1000ft up.i took my cellphone out & videoed what i saw.in front of me about 70 meters away there is an embankment which has a main road on top so i could only see the objects until they went over the top.no sooner had the first gone out of view, a second object appeared and did the same followed by a third & fourth. approximately 20min later i was facing north & saw the 4 objects in close formation zoom off at great speed (north).
